text: Eat half the rice and guess what I found !! Fly on my curry dish. After eating there I’m suffering food poisoning. It been 2 day now I had bad diarrhoea.

A lovely place to eat breakfast! Whole restaurant is generally clean & airy, staff are very courteous and food is pretty good. Ordered prata, crispy on the outside, fluffy and soft on the inside. Fish curry is flavoursome too. Had some ayam goreng too, cold but still tasty.

See their effort in keeping flies away by lighting tealights at food display area.

Well done and keep up the hygiene!
The food is good. The staff overcharge my mother over RM13. Its infested with flies. Spend your money elsewhere. NOT RECOMMENDED!

food tasty, just that they need to have warmers for better reviews
even kopi, teh not warm
The food is delicious… but so many fly , please do something for that ! As this may effect the food quality , please put fly killer machine
